Courtesy #DStv403 JOHANNESBURG - The family of Tyrone Philander is trying coming to terms with their son's death. The younger brother of former Proteas star Vernon Philander was shot dead in Ravensmead in Cape Town on Wednesday. Cape Town police say they are investigating the circumstances around the death. READ:Â Buttler fined for angry Philander outburst While the motive behind his killing is unclear, police are calling on those who might have information to come forward. Vernon Philander confirmed the news on social media thanking his followers for the support they've given him. In a statement, he said the family is coming to terms with the brutal murder of his brother. The family has asked to mourn their son in private.